{"tid":2033823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若bno 平權，作為英國國民，應該利用自己身份向英國施壓","createTime":"2020-05-25T01:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:05:02.000Z","uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e218e94f058050205833a3d3bfafc621deda4e3b","tid":2033823,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"淨係諗走佬就嘥左"},{"pid":"30da05a5b09efff075a74efa34bb454db05fb3ca","tid":2033823,"uid":310166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"難民咋<br />\n仲要寫到明係passport<br />\n國民條毛"},{"pid":"4fbfba1e1fc13df240e3880636b167874da065d4","tid":2033823,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30da05a5b09efff075a74efa34bb454db05fb3ca","tid":2033823,"uid":310166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"難民咋<br />\n仲要寫到明係passport<br />\n國民條毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d065dba608dde57041556e3a37de27bf1685336","tid":2033823,"uid":8776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"30da05a5b09efff075a74efa34bb454db05fb3ca","tid":2033823,"uid":310166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"難民咋<br />\n仲要寫到明係passport<br />\n國民條毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"你分到國民同居留權先翻嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7a0f31cf8652a195b8e1f07e9c0ebb627c2b7b","tid":2033823,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"ac19898f73c7b749baecc3aad8740f7cc292ef81","tid":2033823,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30da05a5b09efff075a74efa34bb454db05fb3ca","tid":2033823,"uid":310166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"難民咋<br />\n仲要寫到明係passport<br />\n國民條毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"有得返工就會砌低懶鬼英國人<br />\n<br />\nBNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}